title: Renew Your Mind | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: Renew Your Mind | Victoria Osteen
description:
If we want to experience the new things God has in store, we have to change our mindset. Don’t be conformed to the world’s way of thinking. Let God transform you through the renewing of your mind.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
